(6, 106, '20251038', 'Many eg Sarrthi IAS, PWIAS Drishti IAS, Level Up IAS, Forum IAS Facets of upsc etc', 'No', 'Not applicable', 'Not applicable', 1, 'Yes I did. I also face time issue in CSAT paper.', 'Many eg (1)focusing on certain deterministic words like \"Only\" \"Some\", \"Can\", \"May\" etc\r\n(2) When confused go with your first instinct rather than unnecessarily complicating it.\r\n\r\n(3) I face problems when answering questions in which \"Not Correct\" is there. So whenever I see \"not correct\" phrase I become extra careful.\r\nEtc', '1) I mostly made mistakes when I tried to think deeply on a question \r\n2) I mishandle \"NOT correct\" questions.\r\n3) Badly struggle in 3 column questions. \r\n4) Difficulty in solving questions which have 5 options.\r\n5) Face confusion in questions asking Departments, years, percentage.', 'Yes I do. In the first round I answer only those questions where I\'m more or less sure. And the I circle the confusing ones or those ones on which I\'m clueless. In the second attempt I mark them on omr and later on check how much effective my MCQ aptitude was regarding those unknown or lesser known questions.', 1, 'Wake up at 9-10 am,  Study from 10 am to 1:30. Have Lunch. Again start studying at 3 pm till 5 pm. Go out for snacks. Again start studying from 6.  Go out for dinner at 9. Again start studying from 11 to 1 am. This routine can deviate from half to one hour.', '2025-02-22 17:17:00', '2025-02-22 17:17:00', NULL),
