(14, 291, 'PCC2025199', 'Don\'t follow any specific, but often use unacademy, pwias to clear some concept or last moment revision.', 'No', 'Not applicable', 'Not applicable', 0, 'Usually not during the mock test, but sometimes during preparation. Everyone doubt themselves at times, I give some time to calm down and try to focus on work in hand, to avert the tension usually, or if it doesn\'t work, I talk with some friend, who can give me the assurance I need at times.', 'Mistakes are fine until you decide to learn from it. And one mistake doesn\'t decide your future. Not everyone always feel positive, but we chose to move forward anyway, that\'s make the real difference.', '1. Not enough revision\r\n2. Not the required depth reached in each topic.', 'I like to go through fast the book first, or the required portion or the notes, and do revision as much as possible.', 1, 'Morning 3 to 4 hours\r\nAfternoon 4 to 5 hours', '2025-02-22 17:34:24', '2025-02-22 17:34:24', NULL),
