(56, 182, '20252041', 'Shivin Sir\'s Youtube Channel, Understand UPSC, Study IQ,Unacademy', 'No', NULL, NULL, 1, 'Yes, In 2023 i got panicked because there is certain change in Question Paper. \r\nin Mock test- In the end hour My efficiency used to decrease a lot, i made very small silly mistake, could not meet the demand of the question which happened with me during first Economy mock Test in SNTCSSC.', 'Need to revise Statics More, some area i am still lagging i need to rectify those are', 'During Economy Mock test-I made mistake about MCLR, Liquidity Trap, SLR, some data i forget', 'Not Really, but one thing i have realized When I attempt 85–90 questions, my score tends to be higher, but I usually get around 30 questions wrong. if a go beyond more than 90 my wrong answers would increase to 35', 1, 'I wake up at 9 AM and go to the SNTCSSC library by 10 AM. I take a 1-hour break from 1:30 to 2:30 PM and leave the library around 6 PM. Then, I go to the gym for 1.5 hours. After dinner, I revise old books from 9 to 11:30 PM. and used to go to Bed at 1AM', '2025-02-22 19:07:50', '2025-02-22 19:07:50', NULL),
(57, 141, '20251085', 'Vision IAS,  Dr. Shivin', 'No', 'NA', 'NA', 1, 'No I don\'t feel any pressure during the mock test but yes in the UPSC prelims I faced stress especially during the CSAT exam and anxiety when ever I came across a certain question which I read bt cannot recollect at that moment and that leads to a chain reaction in the following questions too.', '1. Time management especially in the CSAT paper\r\n2. Via mock tests regularly exam became a part of each week\'s schedule as a result I became much more familiar with the exam conditions.\r\n3. Mock tests helps me to identify my mistakes, area I\'m lagging,  provide me with new informations via explanations.', '1. I have to work on the institutions setup both domestic and at international for various purposes.\r\n2. I have to work on mapping portion.\r\n3. I have to read the statements of the question much more objectively.', 'Yes, I starts from question 1 and do all the question sequentially till 100th question. The confirmed one I tick the option in the question paper for the time and then return to the uncertain question. I try to maximize my attempts of question. In the last 30minutes of the exam I fill my OMR with approximately takes 20minutes for me and the remaining 10minutes I again return to the questions leftout.', 1, '1st slot- 6:30am to 8:30am \r\n2nd slot- 9am to 11am\r\n3rd slot- 1:30pm to 4pm\r\n4th slot- 5:30pm to 9pm\r\n5th slot- 10pm to 12am (more reluctant study slot)', '2025-02-22 19:10:03', '2025-02-22 19:10:03', NULL),
