(76, 293, 'PCC2025074', 'PW ONLY IAS, UNACADEMY', 'NO', NULL, NULL, 0, 'YES, while giving mock tests in the last 30 minutes when I filled up the OMR sheet then I realise how much I had done and then my mind says this is not enough and while reading the questions sometimes the options are giving anxiety.', 'Mock test showing me my mistakes and it shows every time the lack of revision.', 'Wrong marking while filling omr sheet and while in the last 30 minutes to attempt more there is a lot of mistakes while reading questions and sometimes the questions are easy but I could not understand, lack of revision shows me the easy question which could be done correctly but I was unable to recall.', 'Start from question no 1 and start solving, make the marking on confirmed first then sort out which can be done with common sense from the rest and do that and never touch questions which I really don\'t know.', 1, 'wake up: 8:00AM \r\nSubject 1: 9:00AM to 11 AM\r\nBreakfast: 11:30\r\nPYQ and Subject 2: 11:30 to 14:00\r\nLunch: 14:00 to 15:00\r\nPYQ  and  subject 3 and CA: 15:00 to 19:00\r\nCLass: 19:00 to 21:00\r\nDinner: at 22:00\r\nCorrection and marking of all problems of today\'s all subject week chapters and revise: til1 AMAM', '2025-02-22 20:45:36', '2025-02-22 20:45:36', NULL),
