(95, 210, '20252086', 'Study IQ IAS, Career 247, Unacademy IAS', 'Yes', 'Unacademy', 'GS + Optional', 0, 'Sometimes yes. As a beginner, I lack confidence while taking mock tests.', 'I try to appear in all the exams, whether I am prepared or not.', 'Silly mistakes while reading questions due to lack of confidence.', 'First, I try to answer questions I am absolutely sure about.', 1, 'I follow Pomodoro Technique\r\n8 - 10AM : History (Incl. Pyq/qs pratice)\r\n10.30AM - 12PM : Economics (Incl. Pyq/qs pratice)\r\n2 - 3.30PM : Current Affairs/Newspaper\r\n6 - 8PM : Geography/Env & Eco (Incl. Pyq/qs pratice)\r\n10 - 12AM : Polity/ Science & Tech', '2025-02-22 22:07:53', '2025-02-22 22:07:53', NULL),
