(140, 148, '20251097', 'NA', 'No', NULL, NULL, 0, 'I experience some overstimulation from the surroundings and often mark options wrong, or struggle to recall as in recall takes more time', 'Elimination for options, how much depth to have to attempt prelims', 'Marking options wrong, issues in understanding the language of UPSC questions and options', 'I aim to answer at least 65 confidently based on knowledge, general awareness and elimination. Then recently I have started to attempt another 3-10 questions after Majid sir\'s session to build exam intuition', 1, 'I study according to the SNT Exam schedule. Whatever topics will be tested on I study them from the primary sources and PYQs', '2025-02-23 19:48:30', '2025-02-23 19:48:30', NULL),
