(142, 270, 'PCC2025176', 'I do not follow any specific YouTube channel but sometimes I watch Unacademy, Only IAS etc.', 'No', NULL, NULL, 0, 'Yes, I feel stress and nervousness while attempting the questions. Lots of times I feel difficulty to attempt some questions.', 'The mock tests are extremely helpful, while giving the tests I can understand my strengths , weaknesses and time management abilities.', 'I have identified lots of mistakes such as sometimes I am in too hurry to read the questions, sometimes I feel the chosen option will be right, but it does not. I have lack of clarity on some topics.', 'My strategy is to read the questions and answer it as much as I can.', 1, '2 Hours Revision, 5 Hours for GS, 1 Hours Current studies and 2 Hours for CSAT', '2025-02-23 20:03:34', '2025-02-23 20:03:34', NULL),
(143, 237, 'PCC2025092', 'STUDY LOVER VEER FOR CA, GAURAV KAUSHAL (EX. IDES OFFICER) FOR MOTIVATION AND GUIDANCE, STUDY IQ FOR BOTH IR AND CA', 'YES', 'STUDY LOVER VEER', 'UPSC EPFO EO & AO, APFC RECORDED SESSION', 3, 'Sometimes I feel anxious or nervous, especially when I start to solve the paper, usually I mark the ones that will be correct. After that I feel stress if I see that the total attempt in the number of questions is not satisfactory.', 'I came to know the Pattern of Questions, My Silly Mistakes, Both Strong Zone & Weak Zone. It forced me to do some research on the Internet / chatgpt related to that topic.', 'My silly mistake, and what I learned is that I need to go deeper with the subjects.', 'Nothing more than revising the topics as much as I can.', 1, 'I wake up everyday from bed around at 4.30 am., after that at 5.00 am I prepared myself for morning exercise like walking , running etc. After that I return home around at 6.30 am. After taking some rest I take a Bath. And around 7.00 am I start my study as per as my Time Table. I have made my daily schedule, where I divided my study time in 6 parts Two hours per Subjects for 7 days. It is excluding Lunch time and Break time. I take Dinner lightly (at 7.00pm) that\'s why I did not mention it separately, And like this I complete my study at 9.00 pm. This way I start my study at 7.00 am and complete it at 9.00pm. After that I go to bed for sleep.', '2025-02-23 20:07:36', '2025-02-23 20:07:36', NULL),
