(156, 57, 'OST2025158', 'Clarity for upsc with dr shivin\r\nIas pcs pathsala\r\nSansad tv\r\nSleepy classes IAS', 'No', 'NA', NULL, 1, 'Yes, i  got extremely nervous last time after i got the paper and made several mistakes which i could have done right . Yes i do feel anxious especially while taking calculative risks while attempting the questions and start overthinking and get the answers wrong', 'I can understand the mistakes i made, the need of more revisions and from the last prelims i felt that if without proper revision and syllabus completiom I could go that far ,i can  clear prelims if I push harder', 'Need more revisions\r\nNeed to stop hurrying while attempting\r\nNeed to be calm and cautious while marking\r\nNeed to take risks without overthinking\r\nWorking on intelligent guess', 'Attempting as much questions as possible', 1, '8-11 am  gs subject\r\n12-2 pm revision , pyq solving\r\n7.30-8 - 10 pm gs subjects\r\n11- 1  current affairs\r\nHowever concentration level doesnt  remain the same,always so effective study time varies  between 8-9 hours\r\nThis is my study schedule since january \'25 before that i had full time internship so schedule varied that time', '2025-02-23 23:40:04', '2025-02-23 23:40:04', NULL),
