(160, 280, 'PCC2025078', 'Official channels of Vajiram & Ravi, Forum IAS, Vision IAS, Clarity for UPSC by Dr. Shivin, Tathastu-ICS etc', 'No', 'NA', 'NA', 0, 'Sometimes I feel anxious with sleep deprivation which adversely affects during the exam hours', 'I\'ve found out areas where more focus should be given, found my strengths and weaknesses along with an exam strategy', 'I take longer time in reading the questions, lack of a quick revision due to which sometimes I did mistakes in known topics', 'I\'ve divided 2 hours into 4 parts, 30 mins of each segment with 25 questions. 1st round- all known+ intuitive guess, 2nd round - 50-50/75-25', 1, '(9:00-10:00)AM- Previous day\'s study revision \r\n(10:00-11:30)AM- GS (static)\r\n(12:30-2:00) PM- GS (static)\r\n(3:30-4:30) PM- Prev. Test\'s explanation/PYQ analysis of current GS subject \r\n(4:30-5:30)PM- The Hindu Newspaper \r\n(7:00- 9:00)PM- Vision IAS Monthly Magazine \r\n(9:00-10:00)PM- CSAT practice \r\n(11:30pm-12:30am)- Revision of whole day\'s study+ next day\'s planning \r\n(12:30-1:30) AM- Extra time if needed to complete anything', '2025-02-24 00:52:55', '2025-02-24 00:52:55', NULL),
