(162, 22, 'OST2025075', 'Mrunal Patel, understand upsc, ias with Shivin', 'Yes', 'Understand Upsc prevail, Mudit Gupta csat', 'Prelims mock test and notes and classes provided by understand upsc, csat classes by Mudit Gupta.', 2, 'Experienced stress while giving the exam. Could not sleep the previous night so could not focus properly. Extreme anxiety in the last 30 mins did a lot of mistakes', 'Increase in knowledge, awareness about society. Need function properly in times of stress. Questions can be solved through logical analysis.', 'Omr filling and hurry. Sometimes I spend a lot of time on one question and have to hurry on the others. More Pyq analysis and revision is required', 'Solved the question paper in 2 rounds. Tried to apply elimination techniques.', 1, '6:30- 6:45 wake up freshen, little meditation\r\nFirst study start from 7-9:30 (revision 45 mins and then main subject of which the mock test will be held)\r\n2nd study slot 10- 1:00( main subject+ 1 hour current affairs) \r\n1-3:00 break+ lunch\r\n3rd study slot 3-7:30 (20 pyq 1 hour, test solution reading 1 hour, csat 1.5 hours, current affairs 1 hour)\r\n7:30- 9:30- break+ dinner\r\n9:30- 10:30 revision of same day+ newspaper reading.\r\nSleep by 11:30.', '2025-02-24 01:19:21', '2025-02-24 01:19:21', NULL),
