(223, 15, 'OST2025122', '1.CLARITY FOR UPSC BY DR SHIVIN\r\n2. MRUNAL PATEL UNACADEMY', 'NO', 'NOT APPLICABLE', 'NOT APPLICABLE', 1, 'TO SOME EXTENT. BUT RECENTLY ONE THING I HAVE OBSERVED , WITH THE INCREASING HOLD ON EACH AND EVERY SUBJECT NERVOUSNESS IS GETTING REDUCED.', 'CONFIDENCE IS THE KEY THAT MAKE PEOPLE GET THROUGH THIS EXAM AND CONFIDENCE STEMS FROM MULTIPLE REVISIONS AND ACTIVE RECALLING.', '1. NEED TO REVISE THINGS EVERDAY\r\n2. LACK OF CALMNESS WHILE READING QUESTIONS\r\n3. NEED TO RISE UP EARLY IN THE MORNING', '1. TRYING TO CREATE ADVERSE SITUATION WHILE GIVING MOCK TESTS (LIKE NOT TO USE CELING FAN)', 1, 'I AM A LATE RISER. I START MY STUDY AT 9:30 AM. TRY TO COVER TWO GS SUBJECTS A DAY ALONG WITH CURRENT AFFAIRS READING AND CSAT PRACTICE. USUALLY TAKE SOME REST WHILE HAVING MEAL OR EVENING TEA WITH PARENTS. TAKE SOME POWER NAP IN THE AFTERNOON, OTHERWISE CAN\'T STUDY PROPERLY IN THE EVENING.  I AM USED TO LATE NIGHT STUDY (TILL 3 AM) BUT RIGHT NOW TRYING TO GO TO BED EARLY.', '2025-02-24 19:20:32', '2025-02-24 19:20:32', NULL),
