(237, 218, 'PCC2025059', 'PW ONLY IAS, AMIT SENGUPTA, UNACADEMY, Dr UPSC', 'NO', NULL, NULL, 0, 'YES. Stress of completing the paper', 'Focusing on micro themes and going through pyq', 'Mainly I lacked revision, wrong OMR marking, incorrect question reading, spending too much time on a single question', 'Not exactly', 1, 'Note specific subjects, with the specific chapters, I have to cover within a day. Usually I cover two subjects in that day and solve the topic specific questions. Start studying around 7 am; till 12 pm. In evening, from 6 pm till 12:30 pm', '2025-02-24 20:09:00', '2025-02-24 20:09:00', NULL),
