(291, 284, 'PCC2025223', 'E learning channel west bengal.', 'NO', '0', '0', 0, 'I have a lot of stress. But no anxiety or nervousness before mock tests or upsc prelims.', 'I have identified the statements questions,pairs  and analysis many  topics.', 'Most of the questions are negative.', 'I have studying chapter wise  questions, answer follow the preparations .', 1, '8 hours.', '2025-02-25 07:57:47', '2025-02-25 07:57:47', NULL),
(292, 90, '20251010', 'No specific channel', 'Yes', 'Sarrthi IAS', 'Foundation program', 0, 'Yes. I didn\'t utilise my time well. So I am regretting for myself that I have a ability to crack upsc and this is my goal of my life also. But I got distracted. I am okay now but the time has passed. This is my first prelims but I have only 3 months. I am trying my best but i could have utilised my time , I would be very confident for prelims that I am not right now.', 'Cracking UPSC prelims can be possible', 'Revision is required', 'I am giving focus on each subject for studying and revision', 1, 'Optional - 2 GS Subject revision - 1 GS subject Studying', '2025-02-25 10:25:18', '2025-02-25 10:25:18', NULL),
(293, 245, 'PCC2025113', 'Clarity for upsc by Dr.Shivin', NULL, NULL, NULL, 3, 'Yes, experience anxiety and tension which has led me to mark wrong options even when I know the answer', 'Learning the knowledge gaps and the need to do spaced revisions and practice questions so that my memory and intuition does not fail me at the crucial moment', 'Knowing which topics I am confident about and in which knowledge and memory gaps have caused me to use my intuition for tricky questions wrongly and also the false confidence which led me to mark wrongly those questions whose answer I was sure about', 'Solve the questions that I know the answers first, then the ones where intuition needs to be applied and then the tough ones where I rely partly on pre-existing knowledge, intuition and partly on guesswork', 1, 'Study and revise one static subject in the morning.\r\nSolve practice questions and pyqs.\r\nRevise CSAT and practice pyq in the afternoon.\r\nStudy another subject and current affairs in the evening.', '2025-02-25 11:02:15', '2025-02-25 11:02:15', NULL),
(294, 161, '20252015', NULL, 'No', NULL, NULL, 1, 'No', 'Familiarity with UPSC exam hall situation,  numerous revisions, push towards preparation,  confrontation with the flaws,.', 'Many topics i have just read through which need in depth knowledge and need to be explored from every angle, guess and mark need to be reduced .', 'Just going through whole paper fast and then choosing the easier one, starting the paper from last question', 1, 'Studying 4 hrs in the morning and 3 hrs in night', '2025-02-25 12:46:36', '2025-02-25 12:46:36', NULL);
