(35, 79, 'OST2025224', 'IT FULFILLS MY DREAM OF SERVING THE NATION ALONG WITH ENSURING A STABLE CAREER FOR MYSELF', 'DEDICATION, HARDWORK, STRONG MINDSET', 'TO MAKE MY PARENTS HAPPY AFTER SELECTION', 'I DONOT GIVE UP EASILY INSPITE OF INITIAL FAILURES', 'LITTLE MORE CALMNESS IS REQUIRED FOR ME TO HANDLE THE MULTIPLE STAGES OF THE EXAM.', 'INERTIA OF PRACTISING ANSWER WRITING FOR MAINS', 'DIFFICULTY IN ALLOTING ADEQUATE TIME TO BOTH PRELIMS AND MAINS PREPARATION', 'BY DRAWING OUT A BETTER AND WELL BALANCED STUDY SCHEDULE', 'INTROSPECTING MY ROUTINE AND PREVIOUSE SCORES TO IDENTIFY MY STRENGTHS AND WEAKNESSES', 'NEGATIVE THOUGHTS, PEER PRESSURE, SOCIAL MEDIA, CRICKET, SOCIETAL PRESSURE', 'CUTTING MYSELF OFF FROM EVERYTHING FOR THE NEXT FEW MONTHS', 'I WILL TRY TO OVERCOME THEM WITHIN A WEEK', '2025-02-22 18:49:36', '2025-02-22 18:49:36', NULL),
(36, 67, 'OST2025163', 'I wasn\'t happy with my prospective job satisfaction and number of opportunities at the start of my graduation itself and was extensively looking for a career where i could travel a lot, get the power to do good things by utilising my knowledge and available resources, be empathetic and actually make a good use of my need to change things around for the better. All of things combined made me decide to go for this career at my 1st year of engineering.', 'Discipline, Empathy, Constantly Improving oneself, Not losing faith, Not letting external situations affect inner peace and focus.', 'That i have food, shelter, a hunger to contribute to my country and an opportunity to education (2 cr out of a population of 65 cr enrolled in higher education as per AISHE 2020-21) . Another factor which motivates me is the constant ill feeling which i receive from immediate people around me and the urge to stand up even in the face of mental adversities.', 'Memory, Tenacity, Patriotism, Curiosity, Respect', 'I am not very disciplined. I should be less lazy than present. I sometimes give way to external factors and that causes me to waste my time.', 'Lack of proper guidance at Kolkata for further stages of exam and difficulty in obtaining permission to take guidance out of station. Also the constant reminder about age, my voluntary resignation from job and decision to prepare full time and constant reminder that this has to be my last attempt. The second factor sometimes affects me a lot at present too.', 'Family Pressure. Lack of Mental Support and no permission to move out of home to prepare elsewhere.', 'Drawing myself to spirituality and holy books, practising hobbies, calling my best friend, eating snacks from outside sometimes and sleeping.', 'I try to maintain a diary and complete daily goals. I keep a reminder of how many days are left. I try to switch subjects when effective studying goes down in one after long time. I keep myself hydrated to avoid straining eyes and getting sleepy. I start my day with a positive note and withdraw into myself when things get too hard. I believe in myself.', 'Junk food\r\nYoutube videos \r\nProspects of a future healthy family\r\nPresent family problems \r\nThoughts about My poor health.', 'I limit thinking about junk food because it also causes poor health\r\nI set timers for breaks and watch videos in that time only, not other times. Sometimes i fail too.\r\nI remind myself that god has a plan and his plan is that i focus on my career first.\r\nI have practiced retracting myself and going into a peaceful state for years. Now it works around 85% of the time.\r\nI try to limit unnecessary snacking, large amount of carbohydrates which also makes me sleepy and exacerbates my condition.', 'My health: 1 year after i move out.\r\nJunk food problem: 6 months\r\nYoutube video distraction problem: 1 month \r\nRest two stated above, i don\'t know.', '2025-02-22 18:50:25', '2025-02-22 18:50:25', NULL),
(37, 62, 'OST2025203', 'I am in a position of privilege in terms of education and family background, so I would want to better utilize it to change something for the people who are not.', 'Consistency, Discipline, Empathy, Tolerance, leadership', 'The hardwork and support of my parents and friends', 'Leadership abilities, consistent and dedicated', 'Being honest and accountable to myself', 'Handling stress amd procrastination, factual details', 'Managing time and stress', 'Regular exercise and meditation', 'Study schedule, having a focused study group, tracking my hours of study. For my health, I have joined the gym.', 'Social media, smartphone, internet, perfectionism, procrastination', 'I have deleted all my social media accounts. Setup a timer for apps on my smartphone', 'Within a month', '2025-02-22 18:58:49', '2025-02-22 18:58:49', NULL),
