(43, 239, 'PCC2025016', 'I already work as a Tax Assistant in Income Tax Department. Qualifying this examination, will substantially help in my career.', 'Consistency, Hard Work, Stress management and being Integrated in the entire preparation', 'Everyday, I see many IRS(IT) officers in my office. Their demeanor aids to inspire me.', 'I am consistent.', 'Sometimes, I overrely on a particular topic and get bogged down.', 'The descriptive part of mains examination is a bit challenging. I think that in some cases, how much you score depends on the examiner. There may be luck that may lead one to fall in the hands of a difficult examiner who is unwilling to provide marks. Also, in Prelims, the questions are becoming a bit unpredictable at times.', 'Right now, I am facing problems regarding revision and re-revision.', 'By limiting the number of mock tests I give and focus more on revision(although it is more essential to give mock tests and analyse them)', NULL, 'I have no such distraction.', 'No plan.', 'No distraction to begin with.', '2025-02-22 19:13:49', '2025-02-22 19:13:49', NULL),
(44, 29, 'OST2025063', 'I want to serve my country and I want to be in challenging field.', 'Discipline, perseverance, self control', 'I tell myself everyday that I can crack this exam and surely I\'ll do it.', 'I work hard intelligently and try to be consistent at my worst also.', 'I am overthinker , I should stop it. And also I\'m anxious, i need to improve this.', 'Overthinking and becoming anxious.', 'Facing difficulty to complete everyday\'s work and also it is becoming to get hold on stress.', 'I\'m doing exercise to overcome stress and anxiety. And I\'m trying to complete daily task by stretching study time little more.', 'I\'m following schedule i.e which subject to read in which day.', '1. Overthinking \r\n2. I live in joint family \r\n3. Phone\r\n4. Anxiety \r\n5. Health issues', 'By detaching myself from family (except mom dad) & phone\r\nBy exercising & meditation', 'I have identified and I\'m working on it. Already I have started detaching myself from family and stopped using phone randomly also deleted social media accounts.  Started exercising everyday since 1 month.', '2025-02-22 19:14:06', '2025-02-22 19:14:06', NULL),
(45, 59, 'OST2025126', 'I want to become a diplomat and it also provides job security.', 'Consistency, Confidence and Practice', 'Primary motivation is that I have to get my dream job which will also help me to look after myself and my near and dear ones. But also I keep that in my mind that I can not feel same level of motivation everyday and it is totally alright.', 'Willing to improve.', 'I feel I am not confident enough. Here I need to focus more.', 'Procrastination, Under confidence', 'Same as above', 'By following a routine and taking some affirmative action.', 'Listing down the goals and challenges. \r\nKeeping that in front of me everytime. \r\nFollowing a routine.', 'Food\r\nYouTube', 'Mindful eating. \r\nKeeping phone far from study table.', 'Same as above.', '2025-02-22 19:16:54', '2025-02-22 19:16:54', NULL),
(46, 182, '20252041', 'Job Prestige and Stability \r\nDiverse Roles and Responsibilities\r\nDesire to Serve the Nation', 'Discipline and Focus', 'During initial days i used to think how do i compete with the best minds of this country they are from IIT, IMS, Medical  Back ground.\r\nand i am from a very simple background. so i need to proof myself that i am capable of to get into the highest level', 'My parents', 'Communcation Skill, I am not good at english', 'Insecurity, Wheater i am capable enough or not, My friend got last year for preparing for other examinations, whether i am doing a mistake or not.', 'not Really, My parents are supportive, so they give a full freedom so for that time i am not facing any issue', 'Talking to Parents, Weight lifting in Gym= when i do physical activity', 'Study Hard, Be discipline, Solve PYQ as many time, Solve and write answer, Cover Every Dimension of a topic and Don\'t Overthink', 'Social media, Short attention span, Overthinking, Procrastination , Self Doubt', 'Talking to Parents, Weight lifting in Gym= when i do physical activity', 'Next 1 Week: Track distractions, note when they occur, and start minimizing them.\r\nNext 2 Weeks: Implement strict focus techniques (Pomodoro, time blocking, app blockers).\r\nNext 1 Month: Fully eliminate major distractions and optimize your study flow.', '2025-02-22 19:22:21', '2025-02-22 19:22:21', NULL),
