(51, 141, '20251085', 'I always wanted to serve the society in the best way possible so I wanted to be a doctor but consecutively in 2attempts I was unable to secure a government medical seat. So I persuade with graduation in zoology during which I decided to prepare for civil services exam as this service will provide me to serve the society in one of the best ways possible and also will ensure my career growth and diversification.', 'Hard and smart work, decipline, persuasion.', 'The thought of seeing my parents\' smiling faces when I clear this exam fills me with immense motivation. Their happiness and pride are what drive me to push forward. Beyond personal satisfaction, this achievement brings social recognition, a validation of my hard work and dedication. Clearing this exam not only enhances my standing in society but also aligns with my deeper aspiration—to serve and contribute meaningfully to the community. The very idea of making a positive impact on society inspires me every day, reinforcing my commitment to this journey.', '1. I\'m quite deciplined and regular in my schedule.\r\n2. In any situation I don\'t take too much of stress or panic.', 'Sometimes I become quite irregular for 2,3 days where I end up using my phone or reading story books more than focusing on studies.', 'Whenever I score poorly in certain topics, I tend to neglect them during my revision. Since these topics require extra effort, I continuously avoid them until the next mock test approaches. Just before the test, I rush to study them, but this cycle keeps repeating itself.', '1. International and National institutions there setup and configuration\r\n2. Mapping \r\n3. What to focus on about International relations', 'Mapping I will start from March \r\nInternational relations since is a current based topic I was planning to prepare it from PT365.\r\nInternational and national institutions which are in news I will go through them.', 'Mapping I will start from March and I will be completing it within 7 to 10days \r\nInternational relations and the international and national institutions I will go through those which are in news.', 'Reading novels \r\nUsing phone\r\nWatching movies \r\nPlaying chess \r\nWatching cricket matches', 'I had stop purchasing and downloading new novels \r\nDuring the study slots I used to keep my phone in another room \r\nI started watching short films so that it does not kill much of my time\r\nI started Watching highlights of the matches.', 'Reading novels, using phone, playing online chess \r\nI\'m playing less number of matches now and I will gradually reduce it by 2,3 matches per day by March 15th and same for the using of mobile phone.', '2025-02-22 19:39:06', '2025-02-22 19:39:06', NULL),
