(68, 65, 'OST2025176', 'As a homemaker and a mother to a young daughter, I\'ve experienced firsthand the challenges faced by women in our society. Despite being a teacher earlier, I had to take a break to focus on my family. However, as my daughter grew older, I realized that I wanted to set an example for her - to show her that women can pursue their dreams, balance family responsibilities, and create a positive impact.\r\n\r\nPreparing for the civil services is my way :\r\n1. Inspiring my daughter: Demonstrating that women can achieve their goals, even in the face of challenges.\r\n2. Breaking stereotypes: Challenging societal norms that restrict women\'s potential.\r\n3. Pursuing my passion: Merging my interest in public service, leadership, and education.\r\n\r\nAs a teacher, I realized that I was limiting my impact to a single classroom. By becoming a civil servant, I can influence policy decisions, drive positive change, and serve the nation more comprehensively.', 'Discipline, dedication,  hardwork but at the same smart work .\r\nand values  such as : honesty , diligently working on short term goals, right strategy.', 'I see this journey as an opportunity for personal growth, self improvement, and skill development\r\nand acknowledge and celebrate small victories along the way, which helps me stay Motivated and encouraged. \r\nI ONLY KNOW THIS  , that , \" PAIN OF REGRET IS UNBEARABLE \".', 'Critical thinking and Evaluation. \r\nResilience and adaptability,  that I have the ability to cope with stress , adapt to changing circumstances,  and bounce back from setbacks.', 'Managing stress, anxiety and self doubt in a better way during challenging moment.\r\nBalancing study schedule , family responsibilities,  and personal well -being.\r\nSeeking guidance from experienced mentorship offering support to peers.', 'Managing stress, anxiety.\r\nSetting unrealistically high standards, and feeling discouraged by setbacks.', 'Staying updated on current affairs \r\nBalancing study schedule and family responsibilities. \r\nRevision of test analysis of each subjects and their own handwritten notes.', 'Parna Hai to parna Hai.. NO EXCUSE !', 'Giving mock test every alternate day.\r\nReading , revising the test analysis and reflecting on mistakes that I committed on the mock test answers while doing guesswork and related issues.', 'FOMO\r\nHOUSEHOLD CHORES', 'Stopped using social media . Deactivated all accounts except WhatsApp.\r\nCreated a schedule household chores to minimize last minute distraction.', 'Current situation : spending around 1 hours daily on social media\r\nGoal : reduce usage to 20 minutes a day\r\nTimeline:    within 2 week', '2025-02-22 21:06:52', '2025-02-22 21:06:52', NULL),
