(83, 142, '20251086', 'At first I decided to start venturing into this avenue because of my parents\' insistence. But gradually, this preparation journey has motivated me. As I engage myself in the preparation for this marathon, I discover newer aspects of each subject, get to know my country and myself better. I am in this preparation journey because of the dynamic nature of the service, the better lifestyle that it offers in terms of inculcating values like discipline and consistency.', 'In my opinion, values like consistency, dedication, discipline, patience, perseverance and hard work and daily work is crucial for topping the Exam. We can be slow but we must be steady. We don\'t need scholarly academic depth in one particular subject but a sound balanced knowledge about subjects that concern India.', 'My grandmother. She wanted to see me successful and I strive to be the best version of myself for her.\r\nI also acknowledge this fact that I am very privileged. In the race of life, I am already a few steps ahead. I want to put this privilege to good use and give my best.', 'I am trying to discover it.', 'I need consistency and patience.', 'My bad habits. I can\'t effectively manage my time and don\'t follow my plans through , resulting in inconsistency.', 'I started preparing very late and a lot of my time was wasted during my daily travel. The journey also drained me , resulting in no time to study. This created a backlog. I feel like I am under prepared in all subjects.', 'I plan to stick to my daily routine, start revising following the test plan as provided by Sir and start dedicating two hours to CSAT.', 'Nothing much', 'Phone, Anxiety, health, migraine, concentration issues, reading books (novels), bad food at the hostel.', 'I switch off my phone while studying. And I have stopped reading books for fun. (Majorly) . I don\'t have any solution for the others.', 'I will follow the plan. I tend to zone off sometimes while studying. I follow the feynman and pomodoro technique to make recollection and studying engaging and easier', '2025-02-22 22:27:10', '2025-02-22 22:27:10', NULL),
