(97, 94, '20251013', 'Diversity in syllabus of the CSE, job profile, variety of challenges as an administrator', 'Time Management, Social Awareness, Non-biasness, Positive Attitude', 'Getting Employed, Service to the society', 'Social Awareness, Positive Attitude, Knowledge-gathering attitude', 'Time Management, Discipline', 'Time Management, Discipline', 'As I am reading majority of the topics for the 1st time so it takes time to make notes from it. So insufficient time for the revision of the notes. As a result can\'t achieve good scores in the mocks.', 'I am trying to complete the note making in the 1st Mock Test Series, then I will just revise & re-revise them all & will try to solve questions from the topics.', 'I am trying to complete the note making in the 1st Mock Test Series, then I will just revise & re-revise them all & will try to solve questions from the topics.', 'Social Media, Over-socialization', 'trying to switch off my phone while reading, restricting the use of social media., spending quality times with limited number of people, trying to maintain a daily routine.', 'trying to eliminate the distractions before starting the second revision mock tests & maintain it till at least 25/05/2025', '2025-02-23 00:07:39', '2025-02-23 00:07:39', NULL),
