(100, 69, 'OST2025131', 'Desire to do good for the country, Job Security, Career advancement', 'Discipline, Patience, Perseverence, Grit, Determination, Patriotism, Empathy, Social Responsibility', '1. My failures and, \r\n2. The fact that Women in some countries are not even getting access to basic education, so I might as well take full advantage till I can.', 'Patience and Perseverence', 'Overthinking, Restlessness', 'Getting carried away by the thoughts of my friends and peers (of school and college) getting ahead, and I\'m still here.', 'Lack of time', 'By self-acceptance and mindfullness', 'Guided meditation for 20 minutes everyday; and Journaling (at times)', '1. Reading Non-Fictional books and Fictional/ Story Books. I love reading story books. Especially Classics.\r\n2. Overthinking\r\n3. Music', 'I keep reminding myself that I\'m getting old. (I\'m already 23). And I keep telling myself that once I clear the exam I\'ll have a lot of time to read these books.', 'March 1st week 2025.', '2025-02-23 00:27:40', '2025-02-23 00:27:40', NULL),
