(103, 214, 'PCC2025003', '70% of Indians can\'t afford proper diet according to UN FAO Report. Diet means fruits, vegetables, milk, animal proteins. But India is the largest producer of milk, 2nd largest producer of vegetables and fruits both, 3rd in egg production. So we have plethora of sources to get nutrients as well as we have proper Demand-Supply combination. But may be the problem lies in - 1. in Distribution end, 2. in Affordability.  If I want to contribute in this line, I have to join Civil Service, I have to become a part of this administration. I hope Civil Service will give me the power to address the problems and to mitigate them, obviously within my limited capabilities.', 'Focus, Dedication, Hard Word associated with smart work.', 'I don\'t know whether I give my best every day or not, but a feeling of being privileged is something that motivates me a lot. I have proper house to live in, with 24 hours of electricity, water, internet connection, proper connectivity. Candidates from remote villages across the states are also preparing for this exam and I know, most of them don\'t have the facilities that I have. But still they are preparing. What else should I need to study properly!', 'My Purpose. The reason of becoming Civil servant I have mentioned earlier. But I have another bigger purpose. Obviously I want to become an IAS Officer because it is my personal goal. but at the same time I want to secure a good rank for my state also. Every year I use to see aspirants from states like UP, Bihar, Odisha are doing great with astonishing ranks. but my state West Bengal is lagging behind in the final list. I\'m heavily indebted to SNTCSSC for my preparation. it has given me a direction. As it is a West Bengal govt initiative, I think I also have some responsibility to pay back to state govt by securing a top rank. So I\'m trying my level best.', 'I\'m still struggling with the memories of my past failures. Actually I was preparing for Regulatory body Exams (RBI GRADE B, NABARD GRADE A, NABFID Analyst) but couldn\'t succeed. so fear of failure is something each and every day I use to confront with. This is something I have to overcome.', 'I have to try to retain my focus for longer period. Sometimes I lack concentration without any reason.', 'As far as this attempt is concerned, till now no challenge is there as I am still refining and consolidating my knowledge portion. I think after the stipulated 2nd revision and test, I can say something on challenges precisely.', 'Nothing to mention', 'I think stabilizing mind is very important to achieve goal. so I use to do Meditation', '1. Fear of failure   2. sometimes unplanned YouTube videos  only these two I can remember now.', '1. I have been trying to occupy my mind with daily heavy targets to get rid of fear of failure. \r\n2. Watching YT videos when only needed and after watching the particular topic oriented video, trying to close the YT as soon as possible.', 'Within mid of March I hope I can get rid of my distractions.', '2025-02-23 01:08:58', '2025-02-23 01:08:58', NULL),
