(105, 51, 'OST2025165', 'UPLIFT MY SOCIO-ECONOMIC STATUS', 'PERSEVERANCE, DEDICATION AND PATIENCE', 'WHEN I FEEL LOW, I CLOSE MY EYES. I CAN SEE MY MOTHER\'S YELLOW EYES WITH FULL OF TEARS IN HER DEATHBED. MY MOTHER ALWAYS WANTED THAT I WILL CLEAR THIS EXAM. I HAVE TO CLEAR THIS EXAM FOR MY MOTHER AT LEAST. THIS IS MY MOTIVATION.', 'OPTIONAL AND ETHICS PAPER', '1. ACHIEVEMENT OF DAILY GOALS 2.  MORE AND MORE REVISION 3. CSAT PRACTICE', 'MY FATHER\'S HEALTH. HE HAS DIAGNOSED WITH LIVER CANCER LAST YEAR.', '1. CAN NOT PRACTICE CSAT REGULARLY. 2. LACK OF REVISION SPECIALLY FOR ANCIENT AND ART AND CULTURE. 3 IF I CLEAR THIS PRELIMS, I DO NOT HAVE MAINS SPECIFIC NOTES IN GS 1,2,3', 'NO', 'DO NOT HAVE ANY SOLUTION FOR MAINS RELATED PROBLEMS. BUT AS FAR AS PRELIMS 2025 IS CONCERNED, I VAVE TO DEDICATE 2 TO 3 MORE HOURS FOR REVISION AND HAVE TO ACHIEVE THE DAILY TARGETS.', 'YOUTUBE VIDEOS, FILM, WEB SERIES, CRICKET, SOCIAL GATHERINGS', 'YES I HAVE CHALK OUT A PLAN. I HAVE UNINSTALL ALL SOCIAL MEDIA APPS ( EXCEPT WHATSAPP ) FROM MY MOBILE AND DISABLE YOUTUBE.', 'YES I HAVE IDENTIFIED THEM, AS MENTIONED ABOVE AND WANT A MONTH FOR OVERCOMING THEM.', '2025-02-23 03:10:30', '2025-02-23 03:10:30', NULL),
(106, 254, 'PCC2025234', 'I choose to prepare for civil services for to the following reasons: \r\n1. Diversity of work is more in civil services.\r\n2. Amount of experience I will get in this field is more than any other jobs.\r\n3. This service will provide me the platform to contribute for my society.\r\n4. As I belong from a Backward class(SC) this service will not only increase my self confidence but also motivate my fellow peoples to participate in the administrative process to ensure more bright future.', 'Values that are essential for CSE are : \r\n1) Transparancy, 2) Accountability, 3) Compassion, 4) Empathy, 5) Leadership , \r\n6) Communication skill.\r\nEssential habits are as follows: \r\n1) Newspaper reading helps to increase the compression skill\r\n2) Participating in extracurricular activities develops leadership skills.\r\n3) Spending time with family and friends helps to inculcate communication skills.\r\n4) Playing Chess and other outdoor games.', 'I am inspired by the efforts of my parents and how they raise me up for my better future and that\'s why I want to return then something more and beautiful in the form of my result.\r\nI am also inspired by the life story of DR. APJ ABDUL KALAM and his books - Ignited Minds and Wings of fire .', 'My strengths are : \r\n1) Good comprehensive skill\r\n2) Effective analytical skill.\r\n3) I started early and have a lot of time to prepare effectively.\r\n4) I have completed the syllabus properly.\r\n5) My handwritten short notes with current affairs compilation help to revise a topic in less time', '1) Communication skill.\r\n2) Speaking English fluently.\r\n3) Appearance.', '1) Lack of motivation.\r\n2) Mobile distraction.\r\n3) Lack of time as I\'m engaged with a part time work.', '1) Range of knowledge need for a particular topic.\r\n2) Current Affairs revision \r\n3) Time management between college and coaching.', '1) Use a particular book and stick to it .\r\n2) Reading a particular magazine and newspaper for current affairs.', '1) Effectively use my time.\r\n2) More revision and PYQ practice before giving mocks and proper analysis of each test.\r\n3) Limiting the use of mobile.\r\n4) Increase practice and number of revisions.', '1) Mobile usage.\r\n2) Friends \r\n3) Rap Music.\r\n4) Social media ( YouTube only)\r\n5) Gossiping with friends', '1) By restricting myself from friends.\r\n2) I will use YouTube for preparation purpose only.\r\n3) By Limiting screen time of my mobile.\r\n4) Giving more time to study.', 'Timeline - 1 month', '2025-02-23 09:33:07', '2025-02-23 09:33:07', NULL),
