(109, 108, '20251041', 'I have leadership and administrative qualities which I can use as a skill and I think those skills of mine are best suited for this job. Secondly, I am an animal rescuer and I have seen the challenges first hand on how if you don\'t come from a place of authority, people tend to harass you for your good deeds. I really want to build a shelter and dedicate as many resources as possible to the well-being of strays of all kinds: Dogs, Cats, and Cows. This job would help me not only bring attention to their plight but also enable me to find a better place for the ones that I have already rescued.', 'Honesty \r\nIntegrity \r\nClarity in thought process and being calm even during the toughest of situation', 'When I think about my parents and my strays back at home.', 'I haven\'t figured that out yet.', 'In terms of my focus on a particular thing and once when I get defeated, I feel it\'s over for me..', 'My mental health.', 'Struggling to keep up with revisions. My mocks are improving but the input is to output ratio is too disproportionate.', 'By revising more..', 'I haven\'t developed any strategy by myself. I just want to remain consistent with my study schedule.', '1. My parents \r\n2. My finances \r\n3. My job', 'To dedicate less time to my job, to manage finances better by preventing unnecessary expenses. Parents don\'t know how will I manage.', 'March 15th', '2025-02-23 10:17:37', '2025-02-23 10:17:37', NULL),
