(126, 74, 'OST2025231', 'Initially, Civil Services seemed like a good career option. Later, once I understood the work and its impact on society, this appeared as a service to which I wanted to give my time and energy.', 'Discipline and learning from mistakes.', 'Since this shall be my last attempt, this is a do-or-die scenario for me. I cannot afford to miss out on this opportunity.', 'My ability to learn from mistakes and endeavor not to repeat them.', 'The feeling of monotoneity in this long-drawn process.', 'After a few days of intense studying, there are days when there is a definite decline in productivity.', 'On less productive days, I tend to spend more time on my phone instead of studying.', 'Set weekly targets for revision and try to adhere to them.', 'Frequently attempting mock tests ensures better adherence to my weekly targets.', '1. Movies and web series.\r\n2. Mobile use, mostly YouTube scrolling.', 'Keeping my phone aside while studying, and putting limits on app use time.', 'I have been able to reduce my time spent on watching movies and plan to stop it completely at least 1 month before prelims.', '2025-02-23 20:21:56', '2025-02-23 20:21:56', NULL),
