(128, 71, 'OST2025127', 'I like the career profile . It\'s my Mother\'s dream as well as my goal.\r\nNone from my family Ever been to this kind of prestige job . I want to be the first one.', 'Self control \r\nTime management \r\nStudying with consistency \r\nPositive mindset(current here I am lacking ) \r\nHardwork', 'Consistency .', 'I was topper throughout thus I believe I will clear this exam . Also I am from Humanities background probably give me an edge .', 'Discipline \r\nProductivity', 'My residence is exactly opposite of a club where every 10 -15 days have any occasion and they are playing music at high decibel . \r\nHomely atmosphere (Conversation)\r\nOften using Phone .', 'Environment problem \r\nFacing problem with some backlogs. \r\nAfter  a 12hours study session , very next I feel exhausted , my brain drained and then have very little energy cum motivation to study thus then I started scrolling phone because I have to do lot of work which  piles up on my desk and I barely get out of my bed .', 'Honestly I w as think to  make my windows soundproof but that will be very expensive . I use headphones but still that much high decibel keeps coming through my headphones . I really don\'t know . How can I handle the situation.?', 'I am working on it.', 'Conversation \r\nOverthinking \r\nPhone (shorts /youtube content) \r\nSometimes Self doubt.', 'I am still working on it. \r\nFor phone , while I am studying I put my phone in flight mode in fact changed my number also . Thus no disturbance . \r\nBut I want to seek help to overcome other obstacles', 'Okay', '2025-02-23 20:47:43', '2025-02-23 20:47:43', NULL),
