(133, 237, 'PCC2025092', 'In my eyes Civil Services is one of the best option, that provides not only the Job security but also gives us an opportunity to serve the citizen of my country. It also provides a handsome salary which can fulfil our basics needs and standard quality of living in the society.', 'Consistency, Perseverance, Positivity, smartly hardwork, and most important is motivation.', 'I always want to do something for my country, and I think UPSC gives us the Power to do that. Great Power comes with Great Responsibility.', 'Continuation of my Preparation.', 'I need to focus on my Health.', 'Now a days everywhere is competetion , so we need to think about Plan A or B also along with upsc, that\'s Why we need to focus other exam like SSC or PSC. Sometimes other exam preparation might affect the UPSC preparation. But I belief it can be managed with well planning.', 'Sometimes I feel lack of confidence. Especially after looking at the mock test scores.', 'I made my daily schedule already and now with the guidelines of Respected Mentor I can easily overcome all the challenges mentioned above.', 'by staying focused, staying away from negativity with following everyday\'s goal.', 'Negative comments by Others, Friends marriage, Friends Travels, Friends party, family event', 'I have completely ignored them as far as friend matters and other comments are concerned. And when it comes to family events I attend as little as possible.', 'I have identified all distractions and the timeline is \"after my final selection of the particular exam\".', '2025-02-23 21:16:49', '2025-02-23 21:16:49', NULL),
