(137, 25, 'OST2025089', 'Because I want to contribute to the welfare and betterment of the society through civil services. Also I want to work against the social evils like child marriage because as I have a rural background so I have seen broken systems and promised myself to fight for these odds.', 'Positive attitude, mental resilience, perseverance,school student like learning appetite, hard working capacity.', 'Diversity of the syllabus of upsc, scope of learning new things and my parents and friends good wishes motivates me to wake up everyday and study better than yesterday.', 'My dedication towards my commitment, good writing skills,love for reading diverse things , speaking skill.', 'Handling mental stress, anxiety and negative thoughts within myself and negative comments from others.', 'I often think that as I am living in a remote village that can hinder my success but if I can manage my mental and physical health then nothing can hinder me to achieve my goals.', 'Family problems, negative thoughts from peoples ( as I am in my 5th attempt) ,fear of failure, physical health.', 'Detached from family and negative peoples, building mental resilience through meditation, and take proper medication for physical illness.', 'Study like a mad people so that no other thoughts come around me. Maintain regularly,track my preparation by writing all things. Have some free time for hobbies etc.', '1. YouTube 2.peer pressure ( friends are doing well in their life and I am doing nothing stuffs like that) 3. Negative comments from relatives 4.Sleepyness and laziness 5. Loud sound at my neighborhood', '1. Using digital wellbeing app\r\n2. Maintain a safe distance from relatives \r\n3. Make active routine and achievable goals. 4. Use headphones for noise cancellation 5. Have some off time from studies and breaks', '1. Phone- By 1st March,2025, 2. Laziness - as soon as possible', '2025-02-23 23:23:30', '2025-02-23 23:23:30', NULL),
(138, 268, 'PCC2025024', 'I felt that It is a very responsible and multi-tasking job which has the ability to make changes and develop our society and our Nation.', 'Clarity and Structure in all data, Global Mindset.', 'The more I learn and complete steps, the more I become a better person than my previous self.', 'My Analytical ability is good. With more learning and practice I think I can clear it.', 'I am slow and my communication skill is not so well.', 'Essay Writing', 'I have to do deep study to cover all topics.', 'Yes, I am trying to cover as much as I can.', 'I am putting questions and syllabus together to save time.', 'Continuous studying, Routine Maintain.', 'I have prepared a daily routine structure and trying to maintain it.', 'I am planning to get rid of distractions before the start of  2nd Revision', '2025-02-23 23:49:10', '2025-02-23 23:49:10', NULL),
