(141, 57, 'OST2025158', 'This was my childhood dream since my school days  when i was introduced to civil services through magazines like competition success review .especially from 2014-15. Moreover always had the urge to serve the society at grassroots level as well as learn about the governance of the country and its challenges amd diversities', 'Patiencd ,never give up mentality, consistency', 'To make  my long cherished dream from childhood turn into reality and to make a positive impact  in lives of people .', 'Never give up mentality and always being optimistic', 'To work harder and to keep myself calm   and stop being nervous', 'Nervousness, need more revisions,\r\nFeeling underconfident while taking risks making guesses and attempting questions', 'Inconsistent concentration level\r\nNot able to recall things fully\r\nFeeling underconfident while making guesses\r\nNot being able  to stick to schedule sometimes', 'Trying to break the schedule into micro schedules  taking small proper breaks to avoid burnouts\r\nPracticing more questions\r\nDoing more revisions', 'Not to lose hope amidst the obstacles\r\nPlanning things beforehand\r\nGiving more mock tests in exam like time bound manner\r\nAnalysing where i went wrong amd how far i am able to overcome the mistakes', '1.Mobile \r\n2.Once  i  get distracted it takes a while to get things back to rhythm\r\n3.Overthinking while studying\r\n4. Feeling to travel as i love travelling and photography.', 'Staying away from phone as much as possible\r\nTrying not to think about any other thing while studying\r\nControlling the urge to travel  for the time being', 'I am trying to control the distractions as much as possible before the prelims', '2025-02-24 00:10:18', '2025-02-24 00:10:18', NULL),
