(150, 212, '20252095', 'This job gives the opportunity to serve the country while being in the system.', 'Time Management, Mental toughness, Smart Work', 'Encouragement from my family', 'Focus and Determination', 'I need to manage my time more efficiently, stick to a plan and be in present', 'stress and lack of smart work', 'When I am reading one subject, I worry about completing the other subjects', 'allot time for each subject beforehand', 'Pomodoro method', 'Youtube, Random internet surfing, eyes getting tired from too much screen time (for studying purpose), worrying and questioning my decisions, and overthinking', 'For youtube and the browser, I have set a timer. For overthinking, I am still looking for a solution.', 'From now on I am overcoming youtube and net surfing. By mid-March, I will get over overthinking.', '2025-02-24 03:55:17', '2025-02-24 03:55:17', NULL),
(151, 47, 'OST2025192', 'I choose the civil service as it provides me with the opportunity to help to uplift the poorest of the poor and at the same time deal and work with the smartest and richest  enriching me spiritually intellectually and mentally, also civil service comes with prestigious employment and benefit I can uplift my family and help to provide a better life for my parents', 'In my humble opinion the courage to be disciplined the act of being selfish for yourself and your studies the quality of being proactive about things and planning for things in the future,the ability to minimize bigger things or having the confidence to do the things necessary yet having the courage to avoid unnecessary things is cruicial', 'To see the smile of my parents who have given everything for me,to see persons who are dead come out of grave congratulating me on my success to see my enemies  crumble in despair,to see myself eye to eye and tell myself, yes we did it makes me wake up with sleepy eyes , skip web series and movie notifications and skip things a 25-year-old would generally do', 'having good writing skill, having good external knowledge compared to peers due to voracious study habits, participating in quizzes, and being smart  and understanding things easily', 'My emotional state,my discipline life, my sleep cycle,my habit of procrastination, my way to getting things done hook or crook way,sometime not taking the long road I miss out on things', 'having the courage to take on challenges, lack of preparation in certain areas, lack of proper guidance', 'To properly revise and assimilate knowledge and achieve accuracy, the challenge of being easily distracted,', 'Plan to study at different place with people locked in the same path as mine(Ex. SNTCSSC Library)', 'To keep my parents notified of my progress, study online with members,study, and practice rather than just study', 'Emotional disbalance, Lack of urgency, Thinking about other things rather than upsc, Watching content not relevant to life,', 'daily progress report, making myself recall my everyday task every night before sleep', 'before the end of February,', '2025-02-24 09:40:07', '2025-02-24 09:40:07', NULL),
