(215, 78, 'OST2025227', 'Diverse job profile, opportunity to work at grassroot level, satisfaction of working for people with people, social prestige', 'Discipline, Emotional regulation, tenacity', 'Probably this will be my last attempt with full-time preparation. So I perceive this as my last attempt. I see this as a fight for survival of me and my family.', 'Persistency, Discipline, Analytical ability', 'Emotional regulation, focus', 'Anxiety about career uncertainty, financial distress, and ageing parents', 'Anxiety about career uncertainty, financial distress, and ageing parents', 'Focusing on exam preparation, trying to regulate emotions to cope up with anxiety and stress', 'Consolidation of materials and time bound preparation, \r\nMeditation and emotional well being', '1. Career uncertainty \r\n2. Financial distress \r\n3. Ageing parents \r\n\r\nThat\'s all', 'Focusing in preparation, better emotional regulation', 'I don\'t think my distractions can be completely overcome until situation changes. Better I\'m focusing on gradual improvement.', '2025-02-24 19:50:29', '2025-02-24 19:50:29', NULL),
(216, 193, '20252064', 'The immense amount of respect associated with the job. Additionally, the dynamic nature of job gives opportunity for growth leading to job satisfaction. To take impactful decisions and to bring positive effects in the life of others.', 'Hardwork and Consistency in Preparation', 'To clear the examination. \r\nTo become a better version of myself.', 'Support from teachers and family.', 'Developing social skills.', 'Self doubt', 'Lack of time for self study.\r\nDifficulty in covering current-affairs and science and tech.', 'After the completion of the Composite Course, sufficient time will be available. \r\nCovering current-affairs on a regular basis.\r\nCovering basic concepts of science and tech. Covering current-affairs regularly.', 'Sticking to the study schedule. Maintaining Consistency.\r\nCovering current-affairs from youtube.', 'Spending time with family.\r\nGoing out on holidays.\r\nWatching movies.\r\nUsing mobile.', 'To use these as rewards/refreshment after studying consistently( for say 1 month).', 'By the end of Feb\'2025.', '2025-02-24 19:54:39', '2025-02-24 19:54:39', NULL),
(217, 128, '20251109', 'According to me the Civil Services is one of the best platform at an executive level to contribute to the society at a grass root level. Additionally, positions under IAS and IPS hold a significant amount of power. I am a firm believer that with great power comes great responsibility. And this very sense of great responsibility provides for even a greater opportunity to really create a significant difference in the common people\'s lives which has always been my ultimate goal. \r\nSince this exam is in my opinion a sure shot way to directly get started with a role to drive impactful change an legal empowerment in the society, thus i am applying for this exam and see it as a stepping stone to achieving my goal.', '3D\'s- Discipline Dedication Determination', 'My motivation comes from my strong desire to create a meaningful impact through public service, using my legal and analytical skills.  Additionally, I want to be financially independent once again and finally want to have the sense of job satisfaction. In my previous job I always felt that the sense of belonging was missing. I am really looking forward to experiencing the feeling that I am finally doing what I was meant to do.', 'Practical Mindset, Never Back Down Attitude, Resilience, Confident Nature', 'I think I should be working on not doubting myself so much and believe that good things happen to people who are patient enough.', 'Lack of a Disciplined Lifestyle and Consistency, and Haphazard Preparation', 'Health: I had undergone a major surgery last August wherein at first I was diagnosed with 1st stage blood cancer but later that diagnosis got reversed and I was diagnosed with a rare but benign condition called Kikuchi Fujimoto Disease. As of present I am doing much better but the days I am unwell it takes me a lot of time to get back on to my feet which causes a major setback to my preparation. Time Constraint- Since I started the preparation quite late (November 2024) with little to no forethought,it has taken me a lot of time to even understand the nature of this exam. Thus, I feel I am very far behind others & I have very less time. Disorganized Preparation- For the reasons stated above I feel like my preparation uptil now has been pretty disorganized due to Lack of Proper Guidance, Mentorship & Consistency. I feel I still haven\'t completed one subject a 100%', 'I have reached out for help and guidance from Majid Sir. He and I are currently working on a customized targeted study plan which will get me at par with my peers.\r\nAdditionally I am taking the help of my family members to help me work on my consistency and discipline.', '1. Customized Study Plan for each Week\r\n2. Daily Targets\r\n3.Creating Accountability to more than one person who will hold me responsible in case I stray from my plans.', 'Sleep\r\nBeing alone couped up in my house for more than 10 hours a day. I am surrounded by no one of my age and the lack of environment to study makes it easy to get lost in my own thoughts.\r\nPhone \r\nI lose concentration and tend to get distracted when I am studying a subject or topic that I don\'t like', '1. I am trying to join a local library so that would take me out of the house and provide more of a study environment \r\n2.Limiting Phone Usage by tracking the hours \r\n3. Meditation\r\nI need more help in overcoming these distractions.', 'I have mentioned all the distractions above and I want to overcome them by end of March.', '2025-02-24 19:59:00', '2025-02-24 19:59:00', NULL),
