(267, 253, 'PCC2025096', 'This examination gives one of the best opportunities to reach a great number of people with the kind of work one is entrusted in the services.It can lead to both enrichment of my work experiences,comprehensive exposure and a scope to make real life changes in the world which will help in promoting welfare and human betterment', 'Consistency,hardwork, patience and sincerity towards the journey\r\nHonesty and Transparency are two important principles for this path', 'That hard work is the only way for success than any shortcut', 'My hunger to learn,maximize my efficiency and my instinct to only depend on myself for technical execution of my knowledge and presentation of skill', 'Stress management\r\nOrganized approach', 'If any doubt grips me from within or outside,it can be a potential deterrent to the realisation of my capacity to the best of my potential', 'Time management\r\nSettling the huge load of data in a pattern that I can recollect', 'By cutting on other commitments,until they qualify as an important task that requires my involvement\r\nConstructing my own patterns of remembering data in a feasible way', 'To keep my stress propensity in check by Yoga\r\nTo keep patient and be very particular about my knowledge in approaching a question and attempting to answer the respective topic', 'Social functions,phone,short videos on youtube,sensitivity towards bad behaviour, noise of any level', 'By limiting youtube to useful content,by reducing social functions in my list,by not involving myself in potential bad behaviour zones, by adopting sound proof methods of studying,by using cell phone only when that is of import', 'Phone,Social Functions,Sensitivity to bad behaviour,Youtube short videos- Plan to tackle these distractions already in motion\r\nNoise- Plan to tackle this distraction within two days', '2025-02-24 23:16:08', '2025-02-24 23:16:08', NULL),
(268, 173, '20252033', 'I BELONG TO THE FAMILY WHERE MANY PEOPLE ARE/WERE IN GOVT. SERVICES, SO IT WAS AMICABLE DECISION FOR ME TO JOIN AND AFTER THAT OBVIOUSLY I WANT TO SERVE THE SOCIETY AND THE NATION AS A WHOLE.', 'PERSEVERANCE, PRACTICE AND DISCIPLINE', 'I HAVE NO OTHER WAY TO GO. I HAVE TO GET INTO THE SERVICES.', 'PERSEVERANCE AND DETERMINATION', 'DISCIPLINE', 'NOT HAVING SPECIFIC DISCIPLINE.', 'AGAIN IT IS THE ONLY FACTOR THAT I THINK THAT IS DISCIPLINE.', 'WITH DAILY TARGET/S FROM SIR\'S END WILL SOLVE THE PROBLEM.', 'I\'M REALLY STRUGGLING WITH THIS ISSUE AND I HAVE NO PLAN HOW TO OVERCOME THIS ISSUE.', 'OVER SLEEPING, HANGING MUCH TIME WITH FRIENDS, LITTLE BIT HEALTH ISSUES AND NO OTHER.', 'WITH FOCUSED PRELIMS STRATEGY AND DAILY TARGET PLAN, I THINK I WILL ABLE TO OVERCOME THESE ISSUE.', 'I HAVE TO FIX IT THROUGH THE MENTORING SESSIONS WITHIN THE NEXT MONTH.', '2025-02-24 23:18:05', '2025-02-24 23:18:05', NULL),
(269, 107, '20251105', 'Civil services gives the opportunity to help the local people on a ground level and I want to help the women in our society stand on their own feet and be financially independent. Other then that this job gives experience in various fields.', 'Consistency, determination and Hardwork', 'My perseverance and my mother.', 'My capability to work hard', 'I should include some physical activity in my daily routine', 'Since I\'m from maths background my retaining capacity is lower so, I need revise more but this can be a problem.', 'Lack of revision and unable to decide my approach towards the subject that are my weakness', 'I need to revise more and write in a copy after revising for every topic', 'To designate a particular section of my day to revising \r\nSolve questions after every revision', '1. Youtube/instagram \r\n2.Stress/fear of not clearing\r\n3. Chai pe charcha \r\n4. Health issues', 'I have stopped using Instagram \r\nI try to meditate to relief stress\r\nI have limited my time allotted for breaks', 'I\'m working on it and I hope start seeing result by mid March', '2025-02-24 23:29:20', '2025-02-24 23:29:20', NULL),
